# CODEOWNERS
#
# Every pull request requires review from at least one owner listed here.
# GitHub enforces this when branch protection "Require review from Code Owners"
# is enabled on main.
#
# Patterns are evaluated in order; the last matching rule wins.

# Default: all files require the org team
* @Community-Access

# Lead maintainer required for security-sensitive and gate-critical paths
/quill/core/               @accesswatch @kellylford @Community-Access
/quill/io/                 @accesswatch @kellylford @Community-Access
/quill/platform/windows/   @accesswatch @Community-Access
/quill/stability/          @accesswatch @Community-Access
/quill/core/settings.py    @accesswatch
/quill/core/settings_specs.py @accesswatch
/quill/tools/              @accesswatch @Community-Access
/.github/                  @accesswatch @kellylford @Community-Access
/pyproject.toml            @accesswatch @kellylford

# Accessibility-critical surfaces
/quill/ui/                 @accesswatch @kellylford @Community-Access
/tests/accessibility/      @accesswatch @kellylford @Community-Access

# Governance and process docs
/docs/                     @Community-Access
/docs/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md   @Community-Access
/docs/CONTRIBUTING.md      @Community-Access
/docs/SECURITY.md          @accesswatch @Community-Access
/docs/GOVERNANCE.md        @accesswatch @Community-Access
